== 發行 ==
2015年2月6日，環球影業將《惡鄰纏身2》預定於2016年5月13日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Seth Rogen, Zac Efron Reteaming on ‘Neighbors 2′|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/seth-rogen-zac-efron-reteaming-on-neighbors-2-1201425657/|accessdate=2015-07-28|work=Variety|date=2015-02-06|archive-date=2015-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711172549/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/seth-rogen-zac-efron-reteaming-on-neighbors-2-1201425657/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年7月27日，電影的發行日延至2016年5月20日<ref>{{cite news|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|title='Neighbors 2' Moves A Weekend Later In May 2016|url=http://deadline.com/2015/07/neighbors-2-seth-rogen-zac-efron-universal-release-date-change-1201485851/|accessdate=2015-07-28|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2015-07-27|archive-date=2015-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150728125340/http://deadline.com/2015/07/neighbors-2-seth-rogen-zac-efron-universal-release-date-change-1201485851/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
根據[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]上收集的197篇專業評論文章，其中125篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為63%，平均得分5.76（最高10分）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/neighbors_2_sorority_rising/?search=Neighbors |title=Neighbors 2: Sorority Rising (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2017-09-06 |archive-date=2016-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020150307/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/neighbors_2_sorority_rising/?search=Neighbors |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上收集的39篇評論中有19篇給出好評，5篇差評，15篇褒貶不一，平均得分58（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/neighbors-2-sorority-rising |title=Neighbors 2: Sorority Rising reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=2017-09-06 |archive-date=2017-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826052630/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/neighbors-2-sorority-rising |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，在A+至F之間觀眾給的評價約落在「B」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/angry-birds-neighbors-2-the-nice-guys-weekend-box-office-1201760146/ |title='Angry Birds’ Is The Word With $42M-$44M No. 1 Opening; ‘Neighbors 2’ Lower With $25M – Box Office |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2016-05-23 |archive-date=2016-05-24 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6hjcwXJaj?url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/angry-birds-neighbors-2-the-nice-guys-weekend-box-office-1201760146/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在美國上映前電影已在五十六個國家上映<ref name="Overseas20thOpening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/captain-america-civil-war-china-weekend-jungle-book-zootopia-neighbors-2-international-box-office-1201751259/|title=‘Captain America: Civil War’ Rages Offshore With $220M 2nd Frame, $497M Cume; ‘Zootopia’ Crosses $950M WW – Intl B.O.|author=Nancy Tartaglione|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=2016-05-08|accessdate=2016-05-08|archive-date=2016-05-10|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6hOTwPVk5?url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/captain-america-civil-war-china-weekend-jungle-book-zootopia-neighbors-2-international-box-office-1201751259/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。於2016年5月6日在十六個國家上映一星期便獲得了900萬美元的票房。美國首週末票房收入為2180萬美元<ref name=CinemaScore/>。

在臺灣，北市首週末票房為497萬美元，位居第二，冠軍為《[[美國隊長3：英雄內戰|美國隊長3：英雄內戰]]》（2521萬美元）。

